Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A racing second hand,\Na broken satellite!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan's logic is good medicine\Nfor hearts tired by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's a tearful conclusion!\NDepend on him for the case and feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid but\Nhas the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko, Ran, and I went\Nout skiing on our day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, we met their old grade\Nschool teacher, Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and took up her invitation\Nto stay at a lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That night, someone attacked\NSonoko and Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the overdue Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei\N{\i0}was found strangled to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On each of their hands was\Na "mi", "na", and "ko"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon seeing this, Shimoda-{\i1}sensei\N{\i0}holed himself up in his room!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Professor Agasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned there was a suicide at\NHaido Elementary three years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that the name of the deceased\Nstudent was Mochizuki Minako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Ski Lodge Murder Case (Part 2)."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upstairs?! Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay right where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:02:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shimoda-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rope marks on his neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murder weapon isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The upstairs windows don't open,\Nand there aren't any exits!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means it's in someone's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here! Not here! Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the rope is still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the killer's possession!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them has it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure there's\Nno murder weapon, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, look at his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See how he has rope marks,\Njust like Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei {\i0}did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I don't see\Nany rope in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean the killer\Nran off somewhere with the rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was by the staircase the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're still upstairs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just checked all the upstairs rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but didn't find any\Nsuspicious people or rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You checked our bags?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:21.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai Ryuichi Haido Elementary P.E. Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lnteresting. If what the runt says is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:25.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Atsushi (37) Newspaper Reporter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then one of you is the killer\Nand is still carrying the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're not a suspect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get serious.\NThis is my first time upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I were the killer, this brat\Nwould've seen me go downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, whoever has\Nthe rope is the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do some body searches...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:04:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dumb!\NThere was no rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never thought I'd get\Nstripped down in this weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, is it true that\NShimoda-{\i1}sensei {\i0}was murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. A cell phone kept\Nringing in his room next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when I opened his\Ndoor to check, he was already--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound turned out to\Nbe his phone's alarm clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it from my\Nroom across the hall, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I thought you\Nhad a downstairs room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but I moved upstairs\Nafter you broke my door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if neither of\Nus is the killer, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that leaves only Sakai-{\i1}sensei{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're done\Nbody-searching already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he find the rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he didn't! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. How about you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means there's\Nonly one possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat is lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the killer might\Nstill be inside the lodge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Sonoko's\Nstill asleep downstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's hurry to her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never left the staircase!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer is definitely\None of those three!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?! Why won't\Nthe weapon turn up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.\NShe's just sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! It's terrible! Yonehara-{\i1}sensei\N{\i0}was murdered in her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:07:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the killer strangled\Nme with rope, like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, somehow. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess, I'm still a little dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then get some more rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't strangled?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but I had my forehead\Nbashed into the wall instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad you're all right!\NI always looked up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just her! All the girls\Nin our class looked up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overrate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a woman who can't\Ndo anything for her students.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even help you today\Nwhen you were attacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer's to blame!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how the students covered\Nfor you three years ago, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the teacher for the girl\Nwho killed herself, Mochizuki Minako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the killer's goal\Nis to avenge her death,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then it's not surprising\Nyou were attacked first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the same boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in charge of\Nthe volleyball club she was in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, she was Nakamura-{\i1}sensei'{\i0}s\Nfavorite in the Health Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've stopped her\Nfrom committing suicide, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like this murder\Nmystery will continue yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Murder mystery?! Don't tell\Nme someone's been killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\Nit's dangerous to be split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's gather in the living\Nroom and wait for the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! What the heck's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think! There's gotta be a\Nkey to unlocking this mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere in this ski lodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,String?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long strand of fishing line!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a broken\Nrubber band on the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! I've figured out\Nthe ringing-doorbell trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That just leaves\Nthe murder weapon, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can just find that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I've figured out\Nthe disappearing-weapon trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that person is the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how do I tell everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use Sonoko as a detective;\Nshe barely knows what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't use Ran! I can't fool\Nher afterwards like I can Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My best bet is to pretend\NI heard everything from Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then use my real voice\Nto explain it over the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! If I do that with him there,\Nit'll get into the paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my name gets into the paper,\Nthey'll find out I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those men in black\Nwho shrunk me with a pill!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! No wandering off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The professor's weird phone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! He mentioned that my\NVoice-Altering Bow Tie can transmit to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Your phone's ringing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Ran! Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured out who killed\Nthe two teachers at that lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun {\i0}told me.\NNow, I need you to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain the truth\Nto everyone in my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll say it over the phone,\Nso you just repeat it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You can tell everyone\Nover the phone yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, OK. You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell the police\Nwhen they get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll try!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just put this on my ear\Nand say what you say, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back \Nto the others, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna get the person who\Nattacked Sonoko and Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and killed the two teachers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! You figured out who did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and everything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incident #1, in which Yonehara-{\i1}sensei\N{\i0}and Sonoko were attacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incident #2, in which the\Nstrangled Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was set by the\Ndoor to ring the doorbell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incident #3, in which the killer\Nstrangled Shimoda-{\i1}sensei {\i0}upstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and disappeared\Nwith the murder weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured out the one\Nbehind these three incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that that person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that that person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer is one of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A high school girl playing detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, we'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, are you prepared for\Nwhat happens if you're wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd naturally\Nbe hit with a libel suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I put it in the paper and\Nyou're wrong, you'll be expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Expelled?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume you're prepared for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Ran. I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. If you just\Ntrust me and say what I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the truth will be revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, li'l lady?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can write it if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Daughter of Great Mori Kogoro\NSolves Murder Case at Ski Lodge"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the doorbell rang\Nduring Incident #2,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone was here in\Nthe living room but you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could we have done that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that would\Nseem impossible. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with this fishing line and\Nthe rubber band at the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that problem is easily overcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fishing line and rubber band?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The trick is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tie the rubber\Nband to one end of the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wrap the line around\Nthe two pillars by the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then tie the other end to the rubber\Nband while making a small loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you attach the rubber band to\Nthe stiff Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}'s neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lean him toward the door,\Nand support his feet with snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, you measure the line so\Nhe'll stop just before the doorbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given time, the rubber band\Nwill snap due to the cold
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the body will\Nfall and ring the doorbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fishing line would then blow\Naway and vanish from the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the killer murdered Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei\N{\i0}hours before so he'd be stiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer most likely called\Nhim out here and killed him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before we arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Conan-{\i1}kun \N{\i0}saw icicles when we arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Icicles?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Icicles couldn't have formed unless\Nsomeone had been using the heater.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:15:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is an interesting trick,\Nbut would it really work that well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proof over theory!\NGo see for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ski I set up, using the\Nsame trick as I just explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the mystery behind\NIncident #3 has yet to be solved...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain that\Nback in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You're so cool, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait! I'm about\Nto beat your attacker hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, li'l lady. If one of us\Nis the killer, then let's hear about
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the mysterious trick used to make\Nthe rope disappear from upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mysterious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:16:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer never intended\Nto make it vanish to scare us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It only looked that way because\NConan-{\i1}kun {\i0}happened to be by the stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when the murder occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had he not been there,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we would've thought the killer\Nhad fled downstairs with the weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,allowing them to escape\Nsuspicion as they were still upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they set the phone off\Nand had the body found right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were discovered late,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their clever trick to get rid of\Nthe weapon would've been in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the killer was\None of us three upstairs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then explain this\Nweapon-disappearing trick already...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rope wasn't in\Nany of the upstairs rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's still\Nin the killer's possession!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!\NWe searched all three of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But not for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who has it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The one who murdered\NSugiyama-{\i1}sensei {\i0}and Shimoda-{\i1}sensei{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and attacked Yonehara-{\i1}sensei\N{\i0}and Sonoko was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is you, Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She braided her hair like a rope\Nand strangled Shimoda-{\i1}sensei {\i0}with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as if it was real rope...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:18:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as long as her hair is, she\Ncouldn't just strangle people with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if it was a wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wig?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was wrapped around\N Shimoda-{\i1}sensei'{\i0}s neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hair from a wig.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its cuticle has been\Nremoved for easy processing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can tell just by touching...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, with her long hair,\Nshe's the only one capable of this trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be! I saw her lying right\Nthere when I was being strangled!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was probably \NSugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}'s body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. During Incident #1,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she dressed up his body,\Nwhich she hid under her bed, just like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After luring Sonoko\Nfrom the next room over,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attacking from behind,\Nand knocking her out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she hid the body\Nunder the bed again
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and lied down in the same spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After making tracks in the snow
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we'd think the attacker\Nran out the window, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, she would look like\Na victim of the attacker,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,making it easier to get near\NShimoda-{\i1}sensei{\i0}, her next target...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yonehara-{\i1}sensei {\i0}most likely called\Nhim on his cell phone and said this:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I know who did it.\NLet me in and I'll tell you."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a great detective's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, this is a wig.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I only wore it to hide\Nmy hair after I cut it too short.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't prove anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still proof in\Nyour wig that you're the killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? There were scratch\Nmarks on Shimoda-{\i1}sensei{\i0}'s neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there should\Nbe some on that wig...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood that matches\Nhis scratches' perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your motive was likely the "Minako"\Nwritten on the victims' hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To avenge my student murdered\Nthree years ago, Mochizuki Minako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Murdered?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time three years ago,\Nshe came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said two teachers were\Nhelping kids cheat on entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me one was Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0},\Nbut she didn't name the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was shocked\Nit was one she looked up to,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she was going\Nto ask them herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next day, she hanged\Nherself in the volleyball room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I knew Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei\N{\i0} and someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had killed her to keep her quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I gathered teachers she\Nliked and planned this ski tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all know the result. I quickly\Nlearned it was Shimoda-{\i1}sensei{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you didn't have to kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As fellow teachers, they had to pay\Nfor betraying and killing a student
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who had looked up to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, who am I to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I troubled Suzuki-{\i1}san\N{\i0}for my own trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being\Nsuch a horrible teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As agreed, I'm gonna write an article\Nabout that great detective work,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High School Detective Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.74,0:23:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two hours later, the blizzard\Nstopped and the police finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to stop the criminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there was no stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.11,0:23:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the large teardrops spilling from\Nthe eyes of the gentle detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.62,0:24:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuhiko's radio scanner picked\Nup a kidnapper talking on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.88,0:24:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't locate the kid's\Nfather and the kidnapper right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.59,0:24:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something bad'll happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll catch the kidnapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.97,0:24:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely his father!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.64,0:24:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the kidnapper is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in those apartments!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.36,0:24:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan...\N"The Kidnap Locating Case."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.38,0:24:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.67,0:24:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Train.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.70,0:24:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode airs in the new year.\N Watch the movie, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.76,0:24:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a Merry Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.91,0:24:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.62,0:24:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
